  "prompt": "Can I change the nominee details in Atal Pension Yojana?",
  "response": "Yes, you can change the nominee details in Atal Pension Yojana (APY). To do this, you typically need to submit a request to your bank or the financial institution where you enrolled in the scheme. The process generally involves filling out a specific form for changing nominee details. \n\nHere are the general steps to follow:\n\n1. **Visit your bank or financial institution**: Go to the branch where you hold your APY account.\n  \n2. **Obtain the form**: Request the form for changing nominee details.\n\n3. **Fill out the form**: Provide the required information, including details of the new nominee.\n\n4. **Submit the form**: Return the completed form to the bank along with any necessary identification documents they may require.\n\n5. **Confirmation**: Once your application is processed, you should receive confirmation of the change.\n\nIt is advisable to check with your bank for any specific requirements or procedures they may have in place.",
